00:12:46.558 --> 00:12:48.226 position:50% align:center
There's a murderer in here!

00:12:48.309 --> 00:12:50.729 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
You don't sound murdered.

00:12:50.812 --> 00:12:53.648 position:50% align:center
[MIKO] But even so,
I shouldn't have done that.

00:12:53.732 --> 00:12:55.483 position:50% align:center
Yulia couldn't see
the really bad one

00:12:55.567 --> 00:12:57.569 position:50% align:center
that was in the storage room,

00:12:57.652 --> 00:12:59.279 position:50% align:center
but she's telling the truth.

00:12:59.362 --> 00:13:02.490 position:50% align:center
She can see the same
kind of things as me.

00:13:02.574 --> 00:13:04.325 position:50% align:center
I don't want to lie to her.

00:13:04.409 --> 00:13:06.036 position:50% align:center
[YULIA whimpers]

00:13:06.119 --> 00:13:08.246 position:50% align:center
Hey, um, listen...

00:13:11.458 --> 00:13:15.128 position:50% align:center
[MIKO] Except, if I can
see things that she can't,

00:13:15.211 --> 00:13:17.672 position:50% align:center
I could still put her in danger.

00:13:19.174 --> 00:13:23.178 position:50% align:center
Things were fine this time,
but you were lucky.

00:13:23.261 --> 00:13:24.471 position:50% align:center
[YULIA grunts]

00:13:24.554 --> 00:13:26.681 position:50% align:center
I'm still figuring all this out,

00:13:26.765 --> 00:13:31.186 position:50% align:center
but my advice is to
act like you saw nothing.

00:13:31.269 --> 00:13:33.480 position:50% align:center
[YULIA grunts]

00:13:38.693 --> 00:13:41.488 position:50% align:center
I'm sorry. I didn't
plan on hurting you.

00:13:41.571 --> 00:13:43.823 position:50% align:center
[YULIA gasps]

00:13:56.628 --> 00:13:59.214 position:50% align:center
Whoa! Was that a threat?

00:13:59.297 --> 00:14:01.925 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
I let you live this time,

00:14:02.008 --> 00:14:04.219 position:50% align:center
but you were lucky.

00:14:04.302 --> 00:14:06.429 position:50% align:center
So, take my advice.

00:14:06.513 --> 00:14:08.807 position:50% align:center
Act like you saw nothing.

00:14:08.890 --> 00:14:12.352 position:50% align:center
I don't plan on
hurting you, but I will.

00:14:12.435 --> 00:14:16.731 position:50% align:center
[YULIA whimpering]

00:14:16.815 --> 00:14:19.275 position:50% align:center
I swear. I'll get you.

00:14:19.359 --> 00:14:21.319 position:50% align:center
You're going to pay!

00:14:24.989 --> 00:14:28.076 position:50% align:center
[MIKO] I hope we can
talk about it someday.

00:14:28.159 --> 00:14:29.703 position:50% align:center
[HANA]
Hey, Miko!

00:14:29.786 --> 00:14:32.789 position:50% align:center
Did you really choke a girl
to death with your bare hands?

00:14:32.872 --> 00:14:34.457 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
Not to death.

00:14:50.640 --> 00:14:51.933 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
Man, it's late.

00:14:52.017 --> 00:14:55.353 position:50% align:center
Suppose that's what
I get for shopping with Hana.

00:14:55.437 --> 00:14:56.312 position:50% align:center
[phone chimes]

00:14:56.396 --> 00:14:57.522 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
Mm?

00:15:10.452 --> 00:15:11.703 position:50% align:center
[MIKO chuckles]

00:15:19.336 --> 00:15:20.587 position:50% align:center
[MIKO grunts]

00:15:22.255 --> 00:15:25.508 position:50% align:center
[HARUKO'S MOM]
Oh, I don't know...

00:15:25.592 --> 00:15:28.887 position:50% align:center
...where my husband is.

00:15:28.970 --> 00:15:30.555 position:50% align:center
[MIKO grunts]

00:15:32.474 --> 00:15:34.184 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
It's okay.

00:15:36.770 --> 00:15:42.734 position:50% align:center
[HARUKO'S MOM murmuring]

00:15:45.862 --> 00:15:46.696 position:50% align:center
[MIKO gasps]

00:15:46.780 --> 00:15:52.827 position:50% align:center
[HARUKO'S MOM grunting]

00:15:52.911 --> 00:15:56.456 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
It's touching me!

00:15:56.539 --> 00:15:58.750 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:16:01.378 --> 00:16:02.504 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:16:02.587 --> 00:16:08.468 position:50% align:center
[murmuring]

00:16:08.551 --> 00:16:09.761 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
Uh?

00:16:19.604 --> 00:16:21.439 position:50% align:center
[MIKO] I'm seeing
so many of those things

00:16:21.523 --> 00:16:24.484 position:50% align:center
that I'm starting to confuse
them with real people.

00:16:24.567 --> 00:16:25.777 position:50% align:center
Not good.

00:16:25.860 --> 00:16:28.113 position:50% align:center
[HARUKO'S MOM grunts]

00:16:30.740 --> 00:16:32.784 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
Is it this one?

00:16:32.867 --> 00:16:34.411 position:50% align:center
[HARUKO]
Mom?

00:16:34.494 --> 00:16:37.163 position:50% align:center
You can't go wandering
off like that!

00:16:40.000 --> 00:16:42.335 position:50% align:center
You had all of us so worried

00:16:42.419 --> 00:16:45.213 position:50% align:center
and you were running
around without your teeth!

00:16:50.468 --> 00:16:51.678 position:50% align:center
[HARUKO'S MOM]
I don't know who you are

00:16:51.761 --> 00:16:53.346 position:50% align:center
or where you found my dentures,

00:16:53.430 --> 00:16:56.558 position:50% align:center
but I'm wholeheartedly
grateful for your kindness.

00:16:56.641 --> 00:16:58.893 position:50% align:center
[HARUKO]
Hmm. Sorry for the trouble.

00:16:58.977 --> 00:17:00.478 position:50% align:center
Thanks for looking after her.

00:17:00.562 --> 00:17:02.397 position:50% align:center
It's fine.

00:17:02.480 --> 00:17:03.690 position:50% align:center
She was doing all right,

00:17:03.773 --> 00:17:06.401 position:50% align:center
but then she took a turn
once Dad passed away.

00:17:06.484 --> 00:17:09.070 position:50% align:center
Oh, dear. Did we
have dinner yet?

00:17:09.154 --> 00:17:14.034 position:50% align:center
[HARUKO] Now she can't even
remember her own name or family.

00:17:14.117 --> 00:17:15.744 position:50% align:center
Thank you for
helping her get home!

00:17:15.827 --> 00:17:17.495 position:50% align:center
Let me give you
something in return.

00:17:17.579 --> 00:17:20.248 position:50% align:center
That's very kind.
But there's really no need--

00:17:20.331 --> 00:17:21.249 position:50% align:center
[HARUKO]
Wait right here!

00:17:21.332 --> 00:17:23.293 position:50% align:center
Ma'am? Hold on!

00:17:31.051 --> 00:17:33.720 position:50% align:center
I should probably text Mom, huh?

00:17:35.055 --> 00:17:36.264 position:50% align:center
[MIKO gasps]

00:17:36.348 --> 00:17:41.978 position:50% align:center
[HARUKO'S FATHER]
Four, six...

00:17:42.062 --> 00:17:43.688 position:50% align:center
Three.

00:17:43.772 --> 00:17:48.151 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
Oh. This one's not a person.

00:17:48.234 --> 00:17:53.365 position:50% align:center
[HARUKO'S FATHER] Four, six,
three.

00:17:53.448 --> 00:17:56.493 position:50% align:center
[MIKO gasps]
Okay. I should go, right?

00:17:56.576 --> 00:17:58.578 position:50% align:center
Even if it's rude.

00:17:58.661 --> 00:18:00.955 position:50% align:center
[HARUKO'S FATHER growls]

00:18:01.039 --> 00:18:02.624 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
I'm gonna go.

00:18:03.625 --> 00:18:06.336 position:50% align:center
[MIKO gasps]

00:18:06.419 --> 00:18:09.923 position:50% align:center
Young lady, this one
of those internets?

00:18:10.006 --> 00:18:12.592 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
Granny, please!

00:18:12.676 --> 00:18:15.220 position:50% align:center
[HARUKO'S FATHER]
Four, six, three.

00:18:15.303 --> 00:18:18.181 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
It just keeps coming.

00:18:18.264 --> 00:18:21.893 position:50% align:center
My, isn't that fun?

00:18:21.976 --> 00:18:23.812 position:50% align:center
--[MIKO] What's with her grip?
--[HARUKO'S FATHER growls]

00:18:23.895 --> 00:18:25.230 position:50% align:center
[MIKO whimpers]

00:18:25.313 --> 00:18:29.943 position:50% align:center
Four, six, three, one.

00:18:30.026 --> 00:18:31.861 position:50% align:center
[MIKO whimpers]

00:18:41.246 --> 00:18:44.916 position:50% align:center
Four, six, three, one.

00:18:45.000 --> 00:18:47.335 position:50% align:center
And this screen is so bright.

00:18:47.419 --> 00:18:52.924 position:50% align:center
[HARUKO'S FATHER]
Four, six, three, one.

00:18:53.008 --> 00:18:56.886 position:50% align:center
[HARUKO'S MOM grunts] It's so
bright it's making my eyes hurt.

00:18:56.970 --> 00:18:59.264 position:50% align:center
It's a smartphone,
and it does have the internet.

00:18:59.347 --> 00:19:01.057 position:50% align:center
Plus, you can use it
to check your email,

00:19:01.141 --> 00:19:03.560 position:50% align:center
or call people
like a regular phone.

00:19:03.643 --> 00:19:04.644 position:50% align:center
See?

00:19:04.728 --> 00:19:06.479 position:50% align:center
Well, is that so?

00:19:06.563 --> 00:19:08.982 position:50% align:center
I'm not sure who
you are, young lady.

00:19:09.065 --> 00:19:12.736 position:50% align:center
But you are a credit
to your generation.

00:19:12.819 --> 00:19:15.447 position:50% align:center
Sorry to make you wait, dear.

00:19:15.530 --> 00:19:17.240 position:50% align:center
Like steamed buns?

00:19:17.323 --> 00:19:19.034 position:50% align:center
[MIKO, HARUKO grunt]

00:19:28.293 --> 00:19:30.462 position:50% align:center
[door squeaks]

00:19:35.342 --> 00:19:38.803 position:50% align:center
Whatever you're doing,
it'll be easier with the light.

00:19:41.181 --> 00:19:42.432 position:50% align:center
That again, Mom?

00:19:42.515 --> 00:19:46.019 position:50% align:center
There's no way you'll
remember the combination!

00:19:46.102 --> 00:19:47.437 position:50% align:center
[lock clicks]

00:19:47.520 --> 00:19:48.480 position:50% align:center
[door squeaks]

00:19:48.563 --> 00:19:49.898 position:50% align:center
[HARUKO gasps]

00:19:53.485 --> 00:19:56.071 position:50% align:center
Wait, isn't that the
comb Dad bought you?

00:20:06.289 --> 00:20:09.250 position:50% align:center
Well, I'm thinking
pork miso soup.

00:20:09.334 --> 00:20:11.044 position:50% align:center
Haruko?

00:20:11.127 --> 00:20:13.254 position:50% align:center
[gasps] It's you, Mom.

00:20:13.338 --> 00:20:15.215 position:50% align:center
You gonna stand there
stating the obvious,

00:20:15.298 --> 00:20:17.634 position:50% align:center
or you gonna come
help me with dinner?

00:20:19.260 --> 00:20:20.428 position:50% align:center
[HARUKO]
Of course, I'll help!

00:20:20.512 --> 00:20:22.847 position:50% align:center
Just give me a second
to catch up, all right?

00:20:26.518 --> 00:20:27.977 position:50% align:center
[MIKO grunts]

00:20:34.984 --> 00:20:38.905 position:50% align:center
Thank you very much, young lady.

00:20:55.922 --> 00:20:59.592 position:50% align:center
Hey there. Looks like you could
use a bowl of pork miso soup.

00:20:59.676 --> 00:21:02.512 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
Uh! Thanks, but I can't.

00:21:04.180 --> 00:21:06.599 position:50% align:center
Mom's gonna worry about me.

00:21:09.185 --> 00:21:11.187 position:50% align:center
You be safe, dear!

00:21:40.842 --> 00:21:42.218 position:50% align:center
[MIKO chuckles]

00:23:17.230 --> 00:23:18.773 position:50% align:center
[MIKO sighs]

00:23:18.857 --> 00:23:21.818 position:50% align:center
Woo! Donuts are on sale again!

00:23:21.901 --> 00:23:25.280 position:50% align:center
[SHOP MONSTER 02A grunting]

00:23:30.410 --> 00:23:32.704 position:50% align:center
[MIKO]
Was that the guy from yesterday?

00:23:32.787 --> 00:23:35.665 position:50% align:center
We totally gotta get in line!

00:23:35.749 --> 00:23:37.042 position:50% align:center
[JUNJI] You know
that one friend of yours

00:23:37.125 --> 00:23:38.918 position:50% align:center
who's always talking
out of their head?

00:23:39.002 --> 00:23:40.503 position:50% align:center
Well, I've got news for you.

00:23:40.587 --> 00:23:41.838 position:50% align:center
It ain't nonsense.

00:23:41.921 --> 00:23:43.506 position:50% align:center
Next time, episode six.

00:23:43.590 --> 00:23:46.343 position:50% align:center
"She Sees Real Crazy Ones"!

00:23:46.426 --> 00:23:47.385 position:50% align:center
Think you know weird?

00:23:47.469 --> 00:23:49.846 position:50% align:center
Buddy, you don't
know the half of it!